### Não Vá Que É Barril - API Test Requests
### Use com VS Code Extension: REST Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@adminEmail = wellington.miguel@ufba.br
@adminPassword = SenhaSegura123

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/

### 2. Register - Valid Institutional Email
POST @baseUrl/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Wellington Miguel",
  "email": "wellington.miguel@ufba.br",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123"
}

### 3. Register - Invalid Commercial Email (Should fail with 400)
POST @baseUrl/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@gmail.com",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123"
}

### 4. Register - Weak Password (Should fail with 400)
POST @baseUrl/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Test User",
  "email": "test.user@ufba.br",
  "password": "123"
}

### 5. Register - Duplicate Email (Should fail with 400)
POST @baseUrl/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Wellington Miguel",
  "email": "wellington.miguel@ufba.br",
  "password": "OutraSenha123"
}

### 6. Login - Valid Credentials
POST @baseUrl/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "@adminEmail",
  "password": "@adminPassword"
}

### 7. Login - Invalid Email (Should fail with 401)
POST @baseUrl/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nonexistent@ufba.br",
  "password": "SenhaSegura123"
}

### 8. Login - Wrong Password (Should fail with 401)
POST @baseUrl/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "@adminEmail",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### 9. Get Profile - Without Token (Should fail with 401)
GET @baseUrl/profile
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Get Profile - With Valid Token (Replace TOKEN)
GET @baseUrl/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Test Invalid E-mail Domain
POST @baseUrl/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Test User",
  "email": "test.user@gmail.com",
  "password": "ValidPass123"
}

### 12. Test Valid E-mail Domain
POST @baseUrl/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Valid User",
  "email": "valid.user@ufba.br",
  "password": "ValidPass123"
}

### 13. Validate Password Hashing
### After login, check that password is hashed correctly by trying to login multiple times
GET @baseUrl/health
